# Build Loop course doctrine

- **Write target:** `Practical-Office/bml-onboarding` only.
- **Do not** commit Build Loop course/training/docs to `Book-IQ/bookiqv1-rc`.
- **Do not** edit BookIQ services, ledger, or live experiment issues from this workspace.
- **Issue tracker:** `Practical-Office/bml-onboarding` (see `docs/agents/issue-tracker.md`).
- **Wayfinder:** one ticket per session; claim before work; refer by linked title.
- **Lean Startup:** concepts + attribution only — no book excerpts.
